thread.title: Bae delivers big moment in Presidents Cup debut at home

title: Bae delivers big moment in Presidents Cup debut at home
text:
> Sports Bae delivers big moment in Presidents Cup debut at home International team player Adam Scott, left, of Australia celebrates with teammate's Sangmoon Bae, right, of South Korea and Danny Lee, centre, of New Zealand after winning their four ball matches at the Presidents Cup golf tournament at the Jack Nicklaus Golf Club Korea, in Incheon, South Korea, Friday, Oct. 9, 2015.(AP Photo/Woohae Cho) Search Help
